Package gov.nasa.jpf.autodoc.info

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClassInfo
    Class to keep record of common elements of a class, generally extracted from a parsing process to a classfile.
    CollectedInfo
    Class to storeParsed collections of classes, parsed and analyzed.
    JPFInfo
    Class to define specific elements of JPF components
    ModelClassInfo
    Class to keep record of analyzed information of model classes.
    NativePeerInfo
    Class to keep record of analyzed information of native peer classes.
    SubtypeInfo
    Class to keep record of analyzed hierarchical information such as subtypes of Listeners and InstructionFactories.
